                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Rage and Hunter Adrenaline have the same effect, stacking for a total of 85% damage conversion."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The amount of Energy gained from damage taken to Health is affected by Warframe Damage Reduction ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Applies to Status Effects that deal damage over time and damage that bypasses Shields ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Damage taken to Overguard only applies energy if the user does not have Shields (such as Inaros and Nidus )."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The Overguard must also come from an ally . As such, Kullervo 's Recompense does not receive this benefit despite his lack of shields."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Warframes whose shields have been removed via subsumed Parasitic Armor (while active), or Arcane Persistence will benefit from energy conversion from Overguard ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Does not apply to the following sources of damage:"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Self-inflicted damage, such as Nekros 's Despoil or Combat Discipline ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Laser traps encountered in the Orokin Void and Orokin Derelicts ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Health lost due to the Vampire Nightmare Mode modifier, or health drained in Survival missions by falling to 0% life support."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Rage",
                  "pageId": 56485,
                  "revisionId": 2749573,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Energy is gained even with active Channeled Abilities ."
                }
              },
